  "abstract": "The OCC, the Board, and the FDIC (collectively, the \"agencies\") are publishing this joint final rule to reinsert a provision that was inadvertently deleted when the agencies revised their Community Reinvestment Act (CRA) regulations in August 2005. This change is technical only and does not make any substantive revisions. The agencies are also amending their CRA regulations to increase the asset-size threshold to be used to define \"small bank\" and \"intermediate small bank.\" The regulation is ame",
